<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 10:51:04 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>六月</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1eb591e558f</link><description>&lt;p&gt;六月&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="June calendar page. This time, the image shows a close-up of a transparent pill box, divided into breakfast, lunch, dinner and bedtime. Behind it lies a Leatherman. The image is in black and white. Surrounding the image is the following poem in German:

Chronisch 
kreisen Gedanken
wabern wandern wirren 
Sorgen Fetzen Emotionen
ungehalten 
ihre Bahnen 
bauen bauschen bäumen
sich auf
ziehen zupfen zerren
ohne Unterlass 
kein 
verlassen ablassen loslassen
rauslassen!

Einhalt bieten 
brechen binden bündeln 
in Bildern Worten Melodien 
frei
gestalten | machen | sein.
Chronisch kreativ

Translated into English: 

Chronically 
thoughts circle
waver, wander, wander 
Worries, shreds, emotions
indignant 
trace their paths 
build, swell, rise
up
pull, tug, drag
without ceasing 
no 
abandoning, letting go, releasing
letting out!

Pause 
break, bind, bundle 
in images, words, melodies 
freely
shape | create | be.

Chronically creative" height="3638" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a1eb591e558f.jpg" width="2752"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 10:51:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>城市绿意</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1eb262931b8</link><description>&lt;p&gt;城市绿地。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Vegetation, including  daisy blossoms in front, and a building wall, grey, featuring two windows, in the back." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a1eb262931b8.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 10:37:24 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>意大利</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1eaf4b06b10</link><description>&lt;p&gt;意大利&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="🇮🇹 " height="1024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/gianpaolofontani/6a1eaf4b06b10.png" width="1536"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://gianpaolofontani.some.pics"&gt;@gianpaolofontani&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 10:24:14 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a1e9735915db</link><description>&lt;p&gt;里斯本 (2020)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Lisboa (2020)" height="2334" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/hiddenflair/6a1e9735915db.jpg" width="4148"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://hiddenflair.some.pics"&gt;@hiddenflair&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 08:41:29 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a1e80dd94b27</link><description>&lt;p&gt;定制版“大”早餐，不要香肠。炒菠菜和蘑菇确实美味。可爱的沙拉也起到了作用。鸡蛋？超级棒！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Customized “big” breakfast, no sausage. Sauted spinach and mushroom are legit delish. Cute salad played its part too. The egg? Superb!" height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/seth/6a1e80dd94b27.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://seth.some.pics"&gt;@seth&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 07:06:08 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>